This product is a consent-based archive bot for SimpleX groups. Nothing a
group member contributes is republished on the public archive unless that
member has explicitly opted in via a bot command (consent-first).

Third-party components:
  - simplex-chat (npm SDK) — talks to the simplex-chat CLI daemon (SimpleX Chat,
    https://github.com/simplex-chat/simplex-chat). See its own license.
  - PostgreSQL client (pg), dotenv, and the TypeScript/ESLint/Prettier
    toolchain — see their respective licenses under node_modules.

